NK039(ti)008:0: dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti'i bskang ba'i dbu phyogs bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)008:1: dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti'i bskang ba ni /
NK039(ti)008:2: dam tshig nyams na las 'di bya //
NK039(ti)008:3: mtshan rtags ma byung na rnal 'byor pas ma mo mchod pa gal che'o //
NK039(ti)008:4: de la bskang gso bya thabs bya nag lug nag dril nag tsa ra /
NK039(ti)008:7: tshil chen ra ras lu dum rak+ta gsur chen dud pa /
NK039(ti)008:8: ras chen rgyal mtshan phyar dar g.yab dar thod pa ltag sprod kyi rnga sgra /
NK039(ti)008:9: rkang gling dang gser skyems bdud rtsi rnam lnga /
NK039(ti)008:10: sems can srog dbugs tshang ba dang /
NK039(ti)008:11: a mri ta dang gtor ma gtor ma gzhung bzhin bshams la /
NK039(ti)008:12: rang nyid he ru ka yi nga rgyal gyis ma mo mchod cing bskang ba ni /
NK039(ti)008:13: mi dbang rgyal mtshan phyar la 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)008:15: phyogs phyogs dag kyang pha ki na //
NK039(ti)008:16: nyi ma byang shar pha ki na //
NK039(ti)008:17: ri rab ri yi rtse mo na //
NK039(ti)008:18: yongs 'dus shing gi gnas mchog nas //
NK039(ti)008:19: mi ro gsar rnying lcags ri'i nang //
NK039(ti)008:20: thod pa'i sku mkhar ldem pa'i dbus //
NK039(ti)008:21: me rlung 'tshubs ma'i klong dkyil na //
NK039(ti)008:22: mi ro 'bum ni rtsigs pa brtsigs //
NK039(ti)008:23: rta ro 'bum ni gcal du bkram //
NK039(ti)008:24: mi khrag rta khrag mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK039(ti)008:25: the'u rang brgya yi phyag tshang ma //
NK039(ti)008:26: srid pa gsum gyi mnga' bdag ma //
NK039(ti)008:27: 'dod khams gtso mo dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)008:28: bdud kyi yum la gshin rje'i lcam //
NK039(ti)008:29: dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)008:30: ming brgya ma la mtshan stong ma //
NK039(ti)008:31: lha srin sde brgyad gtso mo ste //
NK039(ti)008:32: ru tra stong gi ling pa mo //
NK039(ti)008:33: rnal 'byor kun gyi tshe bsring ma //
NK039(ti)008:34: dam nyams kun gyi srog gcod ma //
NK039(ti)008:35: bdag cag rnams kyi sku srung ma //
NK039(ti)008:36: sngags 'chang bdag gi mchod len ma //
NK039(ti)008:37: skye 'gro yongs kyi shan pa mo //
NK039(ti)008:38: tshe dang srog gi spu gri ma //
NK039(ti)008:39: rnam shes sems kyi sgrol mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)008:40: sangs rgyas stong gi gdung 'dzin ma //
NK039(ti)008:41: theg pa chen po'i 'khor skyong ma //
NK039(ti)008:42: dreg pa kun gyi char 'bebs ma //
NK039(ti)008:43: gling bzhi kun gyi nyu le ma //
NK039(ti)008:44: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i rba klong du //
NK039(ti)008:45: dug gsum phyag rgya bong bu bardzisa //
NK039(ti)008:46: dur khrod rgal stan rga gang du //
NK039(ti)008:47: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor brdal ba la //
NK039(ti)008:48: ma 'dod khams gtso mo bzhugs pa ni //
NK039(ti)008:49: ma tshogs stong gi dbus na 'gying //
NK039(ti)008:50: g.yas na gcod byed ral gri bsnams //
NK039(ti)008:51: g.yon pas thod pa khrag bkang 'dzin //
NK039(ti)008:52: sku stod zhing gi g.yang gzhi bkram //
NK039(ti)008:53: sku smad re lde stag lpags mnabs //
NK039(ti)008:54: dur khrod chas brgyad sku la brgyan //
NK039(ti)008:55: spyi bo'i gtsug na zla ba shar //
NK039(ti)008:56: lte ba dug bsregs nyi mas brgyan //
NK039(ti)008:57: sbrul dang seng ge'i rna cha byas //
NK039(ti)008:58: rigs bzhi'i klu yis chas su rdzogs //
NK039(ti)008:59: khyed kyi snga shad g.yas pa na //
NK039(ti)008:60: bdud kyi khram bam nag po bkal //
NK039(ti)008:61: song phod deng sang su 'chi na //
NK039(ti)008:62: do tshigs khyod kyi khram la thob //
NK039(ti)008:63: khyed kyi snga shad g.yon pa na //
NK039(ti)008:64: nad kyi rkyal pa sngo dmar bkal //
NK039(ti)008:65: song phod deng sang su 'chi ba //
NK039(ti)008:66: khyod kyi nad rkyal kha phyes la //
NK039(ti)008:67: sbrul nag lnga brgya'i kha 'ching khrol //
NK039(ti)008:68: dam nyams sdang ba'i dgra bo la //
NK039(ti)008:69: nad kyi rkyal pa kha phyes shig /
NK039(ti)008:70: khyod kyi mchan khung g.yas pa na //
NK039(ti)008:71: bdud kyi shwa rdil dkar nag bkram //
NK039(ti)008:72: song phod do tshigs su 'chi na //
NK039(ti)008:73: khyod kyi shwa rdil dkar nag khroms //
NK039(ti)008:74: khyod kyi mchan khung g.yon pa na //
NK039(ti)008:75: byang dmar rtsis kyi byang bu sbas //
NK039(ti)008:76: song phod do tshigs su 'chi na //
NK039(ti)008:77: do tshigs khyod kyi rtsis la thobs //
NK039(ti)008:78: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)008:79: dam rdzas mdos kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)008:80: tshogs kyi gtor mas thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)008:81: dmar chen ar+g+hamsa thugs dam bskang //
NK039(ti)008:82: gsur chen dud pas thugs srog med dbugs kyi dbugs
NK039(ti)008:83: med srog gis bskang ngo mchod do mnyes pa dgu
NK039(ti)008:84: yis shel sgong nag pos tsa ra lug gis mkha'
NK039(ti)008:85: lding nag pos bskang ngo mchod do rmad byung gtor
NK039(ti)008:86: mas dbang po rnam lngas mi dbang 'bras smin byang
NK039(ti)008:87: chub sems kyis 'dod pa du mas a mri ta
NK039(ti)008:88: yis bskang ngo bskang ba 'di yis byin rlabs kyis
NK039(ti)008:89: // bdag cag spun dang ming sring dang //
NK039(ti)008:90: mched dang lcam dral 'khor bcas kyi //
NK039(ti)008:91: nyams pa thams cad sor chud nas //
NK039(ti)008:92: bkrag dang gzi mdangs rgyas par mdzod //
NK039(ti)008:93: tshe dang dbang thang dar bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)008:94: dkor nor longs spyod 'phel bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)008:95: sdang ba'i dgra la rtags phyung zhig /
NK039(ti)008:96: gnod pa'i bgegs la las mdzod cig /
NK039(ti)008:97: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)008:98: 'di sngon tshe gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa la
NK039(ti)008:99: smon lam btab phyir rnal 'byor pa dam tshig dang
NK039(ti)008:100: ldan pa rnams kyis ma mo mchod na rtag tu
NK039(ti)008:102: gsang sngags spyi yi srung ma chen po'o //
